summary: Completed comprehensive testing of TranscriptorIA app. Frontend UI works correctly with proper pricing (10 CHF/month), user registration/login flows, and modal centering. Backend APIs are functional but admin access is blocked due to unknown password. Subscription system is properly implemented requiring active subscription for project creation.

authentication_issues.issue: Cannot login as admin@transcriptoria.com - password unknown

subscription_requirements.issue: Returns 403 'Active subscription required' for non-subscribed users
subscription_requirements.impact: Expected behavior - users need subscription to create projects

passed_tests: Landing page shows 'Voir les tarifs' button (not 'Commencer gratuitement')
Pricing page displays 10 CHF/month plan correctly
User registration flow works and redirects to pricing
Dashboard access properly protected (redirects to auth when not logged in)

success_percentage.backend: 75% - Core functionality works, admin access blocked

action_item_for_main_agent: Admin login credentials needed to test admin functionality (/admin page, user management). Current admin@transcriptoria.com password is unknown. All other core features are working correctly.
